# Containers and Platform Engineering

Owners: Container and Orchestration Engineer and Platform Product and Developer Experience Engineer.

Cover Docker, OCI images, Docker Compose, Kubernetes workloads, Helm, Kustomize, registries, internal developer platforms, catalogs, portals, templates, golden paths, and platform-as-a-product contracts.

Use `.cursor/skills/containers-platform-engineering/SKILL.md` and `docs/containers-platform-engineering-workflows.md`.

Stop on requested image build, container run, cluster apply, registry mutation, platform API call, unsafe self-service, embedded secrets, real endpoints, or missing human approval.
